petrobra see rai export of fuel in 1987 brazil 's state oil compani petrobra is pledg to export 4.6 mln cubic meter of fuel , or 28.9 mln barrel in 1987 , a compani spokesman said . he said that repr a total sale worth 600 mln dlr . the volum is 27 pct higher over 1986 sale , which total 3.6 mln cubic meter , or 22.6 mln barrel . the unit state , africa and latin american are brazil ' main fuel buyer , the spokesman said .